headline: Fifth Third (FITB): Assessing Valuation After a Strong Share Price Run and Long-Term Total Return
summary: Fifth Third Bancorp (FITB) has quietly delivered a strong run this month, and investors are starting to ask whether the recent momentum still leaves room for value or if expectations are getting ahead of fundamentals. See our latest analysis for Fifth Third Bancorp.
